<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Services</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        .service-divider {
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .service-icon {
            width: 300px; 
            height: 150px; 
        }
    </style>
    <link rel="icon" href="/img/logo.png" type="image/x-icon">

</head>
<body>

<%- include('partials/navbar') %>

<div class="container mt-5" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
    <h2 style="color: #333;">Services</h2>
    <p style="color: #666;">I offer a range of services based on my skills and expertise. Here's how I can help you:</p>

    <!-- Service 1: C# and Java Development -->
    <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <img src="/img/coding.jpg" alt="C# and Java Development" class="img-fluid service-icon">
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-9">
            <h3>C# and Java Development</h3>
            <p>
                I specialize in C# and Java application development. Whether you need a desktop application, a mobile app, or a web-based solution, I can bring your ideas to life using these powerful programming languages.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr class="service-divider"> 

    <!-- Service 2: Oracle SQL and Database Management -->
    <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <img src="/img/database.png" alt="Oracle SQL and Database Management" class="img-fluid service-icon">
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-9">
            <h3>Oracle SQL and Database Management</h3>
            <p>
                I have extensive experience in Oracle SQL and database management. Whether it's designing, optimizing, or maintaining databases, I can ensure your data is organized and accessible for your applications.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr class="service-divider"> 

    <!-- Service 3: Web Development with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript -->
    <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <img src="/img/webdev.png" alt="Web Development with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript" class="img-fluid service-icon">
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-9">
            <h3>Web Development with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript</h3>
            <p>
                I excel in web development using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Whether you need a stunning website, a dynamic web application, or user interface enhancements, I can create engaging web experiences.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
